{"type": "article", "id": 1406, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2014-07-09T11:25:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1609, "name": "拟人家具"}, {"id": 1610, "name": "有机摩天大楼"}, {"id": 1328, "name": "灯"}, {"id": 1611, "name": "冲浪板"}, {"id": 1612, "name": "Mac"}], "category": 17, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604224826vacj0DHyXh2tRSNL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">1.  拟人家具</span> by <a href=\"http://www.dam.pt\" target=\"_blank\">DAM &amp; Friends</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t吹胡子瞪眼的挂钟、一脸惊讶的床头柜、木呆呆的电视柜，家具们被赋予了拟人化的表情，生动可爱，独居的住客有了它们的陪伴也能少点寂寞吧。<a href=\"http://www.dam.pt/?p=products\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224820fbBy2l9SFWJPdRin.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224820zTHAhYKupyD1dlks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042248219Qm2jenVUikBu6s4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">2.  有机摩天大楼</span> by <a href=\"http://chartcorb.free.fr\" target=\"_blank\">Thomas Corbasson</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t这个长得笋一样的建筑，是设计师<span class=\"s5\"> Thomas Corbasson </span>为伦敦设计的，它不仅仅是外形像笋，而是随着楼内居民丢弃越来越多的玻璃和纸张垃圾，这座建筑物的像笋一样长高，换句话说，接下来的楼是用居民产生的垃圾加高的。预计所需要的“垃圾”将在一年内产生。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224821edwOgJiMz4f3CTay.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t3.  BAMBOO by Antoni Arola &amp; Enric Rodríguez\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t名为竹节的装饰灯，白色细长又略带倾斜角度的灯柱就像丛生的竹子，不同方向的灯筒像四周投射光线，层次丰富，营造出宁静的气氛。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224822Z8BPUX6slWbmeqYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042248225KXxvH0W6znYktO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224823hVijwGMWdEO7mNpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t4.  Fish Surfboard by <a href=\"http://octovo.com\" target=\"_blank\">Octovo</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t鱼造型的冲浪板，有五种不同的形状可选，每只冲浪板都由手工塑形的泡沫塑料和可定制的木质皮肤组成，并搭配可定制的冲浪板提袋。骑上这款冲浪板像鱼儿一样享受水上快乐吧。<a href=\"http://octovo.com/off-map/off-map-with-jason-tilley/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224824nrgIdWXtN8GEApa0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042248249nU1XsPiJCIRbFYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224825MuaOHqEdvbDnL6CX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t5.  Marge Simpson x MAC collection by <a href=\"http://www.maccosmetics.com/index.tmpl\" target=\"_blank\">MAC</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t今年<span class=\"s5\"> 7 </span>月<span class=\"s5\"> 26 </span>日在圣地亚哥举行的<span class=\"s5\"> Comic-Con </span>上，专业彩妆品牌<span class=\"s5\"> MAC </span>即将推出与著名动画人物玛吉·辛普森的合作款（终于知道一向严谨的<span class=\"s5\"> Sheldon </span>为何为了 <span class=\"s5\">Comic-Con </span>都要考虑买黄牛票了）。该系列一共十款产品，包括眼影盘、唇彩、腮红、假睫毛等等，价格从<span class=\"s5\"> 16.5 </span>美元到<span class=\"s5\"> 44 </span>美元。最终这套限量彩妆将在 <span class=\"s5\">8 </span>月底正式在<span class=\"s5\"> <a href=\"http://www.maccosmetics.com\" target=\"_blank\">MAC </a></span><a href=\"http://www.maccosmetics.com\" target=\"_blank\">线上</a>和实体店开卖，辛普森迷们不能错过。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224825sQWwAr1yhiJpgmtK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}